 the consumers resident in the area.
 Any positive externality from being in a richer reason is interpreted as
 utility from merely being in a reference 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{1}$
\end_inset

 rather than 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{2}$
\end_inset

 where the richness in 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{1}$
\end_inset

