\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

 
\bar default
are important control in the above analyses.
 The households in later stages (i.e.
 households with an older household-head) may be less likely to be interested
 in preparedness for the next reference.
 The inertia to preparedness through expenditure 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi(r,t)$
\end_inset

 may also be due to higher assets 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta(t,\rho)$
\end_inset

 or specific 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

 (e.g.
